    "asOf": "2022-04-07",
    "date": "2022-09-20T17:19:25Z",
    "text": "Discounted Drugs for Clinical Trials Act\n\nThis bill allows researchers to obtain certain high-cost drugs and biologics at discounted prices from manufacturers. Researchers must apply to the Food and Drug Administration for approval; manufacturers must sell the approved quantity of drugs to researchers at the discounted price and are subject to civil actions from researchers for noncompliance."
